 <hr>
 You cannot keep motivation if you feel pressure from external factors. Motivation that comes from within you can be maintained to some extent.
 We do not play with the encouragement of being seen. We do not lose heart even if we are not seen.
 The results do not necessarily correspond to being satisfied with what you are getting. Discrepancies.
 If you practice doing something without sleep, you won't be in a hurry if you can't sleep before an important event.
 Devices to minimize unevenness in mental and physical conditions
 If you look back at the past, you may feel old. But if you look at yourself only now, you will never feel old.
 Not much progress can be expected from change without sacrifice.
 It's easy to lose yourself when you're worried about the way others look at you.
 There's no point in worrying about things that don't necessarily convey your true intentions.
 Bottega bags do not have any recognizable brand markings at a glance.
 Status and position are not important to a real professional. What is important is quality performance and work, and the preparation to produce it.
 Showing off hidden techniques is not always a kindness. It is a fan's prerogative to speculate.
 The goal is "to feel that you have done all you can do.
 You are expected to fail, so you will not lose motivation if you fail.
 We all have times when we are not in good shape. But I don't think we can admit that we are not in good shape.
 People who say to others, "He needs to peel off his skin already," think they are finished. I don't want to be like that.
 When in a slump, do not try to remember your best condition. Make it your goal to get back to average.
 I'm working hard" is something you have other people say, not something you say yourself.
